- In `future_schedule_callbacks`:
    - In the loop:
      ```c
      for (Py_ssize_t i = 0; i < n; i++) {
          ...
          Py_INCREF(fut);
          if (call_soon(..., (PyObject*)fut, ...)) {
              Py_DECREF(fut);
              ... // error
          }
          Py_DECREF(fut);
      }
      ```

